less%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20a%20similar%20event%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20Others%20are%20in%20the%20works%20in%20cities%20across%20the%20US%2C%20including%20in%20Miami%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20social%20media%2C%20the%20summit%20was%20touted%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_aqbjCycVq%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20gathering%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20live%20healthier%20(and%20maybe%20even%20forever)%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20From%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20interest%20in%20longevity%20is%20high%20enough%20to%20sell%20out%20events%20like%20this%2C%20for%20which%20tickets%20cost%20from%20%24179%20to%20%24599.%20The%20%26quot%3BDon't%20Die%26quot%3B%20summit%20organizers%20provided%20Business%20Insider%20with%20access%20to%20attend%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20and%20his%20company%2C%20Blueprint%2C%20featured%20prominently%2C%20and%20so%20did%20his%20friends%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0six%20other%20men%20and%20one%20woman%20on%20the%20speaker%20lineup.%20Coinbase's%20former%20chief%20technology%20officer%20Balaji%20Srinivasan%20even%20talked%20about%20how%20he%20planned%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20an%20actual%20'Don't%20Die'%20community%26quot%3B%20at%20his%20three-month%20crypto-focused%20%26quot%3Bschool%26quot%3B%20for%20adults%20in%20nearby%20Malaysia.%20There%2C%20students%20would%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbalajis.com%2Fp%2Fnetwork-school%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlueprint-inspired%20workouts%20and%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20by%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20summit%20was%20billed%20as%20possibly%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDontDieSummit%2Fstatus%2F1831717503883714756%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20most%20important%20day%20of%20your%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20talks%20were%20less%20in-depth%20than%20I%20had%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20no%20l