%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%242%20million-a-year%20quest%20to%20reverse%20the%20aging%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20possibly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-escape-velocity-what-is-it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20forever%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20calls%20this%20experiment%20%26quot%3BProject%20Blueprint%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20includes%20unusual%20practices%20like%20consuming%20over%20100%20supplement%20pills%20every%20day%2C%20blasting%20his%20body%20with%20red%20light%2C%20and%20sleeping%20with%20a%20device%20attached%20to%20his%20penis%20to%20monitor%20his%20nighttime%20erections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20manner%20fitting%20his%20eccentricity%2C%20Johnson%20also%20briefly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-bryan-johnson-swapped-blood-with-teenage-son-young-blood-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfused%20himself%20with%20the%20blood%20of%20his%20teenage%20son%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20although%20he%20says%20he%20has%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-bryan-johnson-stops-blood-infusions-young-people-teen-son-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estopped%20the%20practice%20after%20not%20seeing%20any%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2023-01-25%2Fanti-aging-techniques-taken-to-extreme-by-bryan-johnson%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20profile%20last%20year%2C%20Johnson%20and%20his%20doctors%20claimed%20that%20test%20results%20have%20suggested%20that%20he%20has%20the%20heart%20of%20a%2037-year-old%2C%20the%20skin%20of%20a%2028-year-old%2C%20and%20the%20lung%20capacity%20of%20an%2018-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20scientists%20and%20medical%20professionals%20are%20unconvinced%20that%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-millionaire-5-years-anti-ageing-routine-brian-johnson-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20parts%20of%20Johnson's%20extensive%20routine%20are%20as%20effective%20as%20he%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Dr.%20Andrea%20Maier%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20medicine%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20studies%20involving%20health%20supplements%20usually%20test%20the%20efficacy%20of%20just%20one%20supplement%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20mixture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20studies%20showcasing%20whether%20a%20mixture%20of%20supplements%20is%20beneficial%20to%20optimize%20health%20or%20not.%20And%20they%20might%20even%20be%20detrimental%20because%20one%20supplement%20might%20do%20one%20thing%20and%20another%20might%20do%20something%20else%2C%20which%20might%20not%20go%20well%20within%20a%20cell%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20while%20wellness%20techniques%20like%20ice%20baths%20and%20red%20light%20therapy%20are%20popular%2C%20there%20is%20insufficient%20evidence%20to%20prove%20their%20positive%20effects%20on%20longevity.%20An%20ice%20bath%20may%20even%20be%20harmful%20to%20some%20since%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20hype%20in%20our%20field%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20so%20it's%20better%20to%20rely%20on%20evidence-based%20approaches%20and%20be%20a%20little%20cautious%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20some%20of%20these%20interventions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eadding%20that%20she%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5f97554-a960-4f16-a636-2ac989611194%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20of%20longevity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20Johnson%20from%20trying%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20fear%20of%20aging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20company%20Blueprint%2C%20Johnson%20peddles%20wellness%20products%20such%20as%20a%2