5C%22%3E94%25-%20Most%20of%20the%20flour%20was%20picked%20up%20on%20the%20first%20swipe%2C%20but%20there%20were%20visible%20streaks%20and%20small%20clumps%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E100%25%20-%20Sucked%20up%20all%20particles%20completely%20on%20Auto%3B%20struggled%20with%20eco%20mode.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ELevoit%20LVAC-200%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E100%25%20-%20Fully%20picked%20up%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E94%25%20-%20A%20little%20residue%20left%20over%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Battery%20life%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20battery%20life%20of%20cordless%20vacuums%20often%20varies%20significantly%20from%20the%20marketed%20runtime%2C%20so%20we%20test%20each%20vacuum%20to%20see%20how%20long%20the%20vacuum%20realistically%20lasts%20during%20use.%20Starting%20with%20a%20full%20charge%2C%20we%20run%20each%20vacuum%20on%20its%20normal%20setting%20until%20it%20dies.%20If%20the%20vacuum%20has%20a%20boost%20mode%2C%20we%20repeat%20the%20test%20to%20see%20the%20runtime%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Comfort%20and%20ease%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20testing%20each%20vacuum%2C%20we%20consider%20its%20ergonomics%2C%20weight%2C%20and%20overall%20comfort.%20Some%20of%20the%20factors%20we%20evaluate%20include%3A%20how%20tiring%20it%20is%20to%20hold%2C%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20maneuver%2C%20and%20the%20effort%20required%20to%20activate%20the%20power%20button.%20We%20also%20note%20whether%20it%20can%20fit%20under%20low%20spaces%20and%20any%20additional%20helpful%20features%20like%20a%20headlight%20to%20illuminate%20your%20cleaning%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Disposal%20method%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDuring%20each%20cleaning%20session%2C%20we%20evaluate%20the%20size%2C%20cleanliness%2C%20and%20ease%20of%20emptying%20the%20dustbin.%20We%20note%20how%20often%20we%20had%20to%20empty%20the%20bin%2C%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20open%2C%20and%20whether%20any%20debris%20gets%20stuck%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20fished%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Storage%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFinally%2C%20we%20consider%20how%20easy%20each%20vacuum%20is%20to%20store.%20For%20models%20that%20come%20with%20a%20dock%2C%20we%20consider%20ease%20of%20installation%20and%20stability%2C%20as%20well%20as%20whether%20there%20are%20storage%20slots%20for%20the%20vacuum's%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Warranty%20and%20customer%20service%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20registered%20each%20vacuum%2C%20noted%20warranty%20terms%2C%20and%20spoke%20to%20customer%20service%20reps%20to%20evaluate%20the%20ease%20of%20registration%20and%20quality%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECordless%20vacuum%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holds%20a%20dirty%20filter%20from%20a%20cordless%20vacuum%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6054f773cad7d300183f81f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHere's%20your%20sign%20to%20check%20and%20clean%20your%20vacuum%20filter.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20cordless%20vacuums%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20a%20vacuum%20that's%20smaller%20and%20more%20convenient%20to%20use%20for%20day-to-day%20cleaning%2C%20a%20cordless%20vacuum%20is%20generally%20the%20way%20to%20go.%20These%20battery-powered%20models%20are%20lighter%20and%20more%20mobile%20than%20upright%20or%20canister%20vacuums%2C%20and%20because%20you're%20not%20tethered%20by%20a%20power%20cord%2C%20you%20can%20quickly%20suck%20up%20all%20kinds%20of%20messes%2C%20from%20small%20spills%20to%20spider%20webs%20in%20the%20corners%20of%20your%20home.%20Some%20of%20today's%20best%20