g%2C%20and%20the%20Radical%20Democrats%20throughout%20the%20Deep%20State%20are%20freaking%20out.%20This%20entire%20case%20is%20a%20partisan%2C%20Unconstitutional%20Witch%20Hunt%20that%20should%20be%20dismissed%20entirely%2C%20together%20with%20ALL%20of%20the%20remaining%20Democrat%20hoaxes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThese%20are%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20takeaways%20from%20the%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Pence%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6565f7f1c58b6f84123ae09a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMike%20Pence.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d3319d1-efe2-4f1e-8827-7459ae148884%5C%22%3EThe%20Pence%20pressure%20campaign%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20is%20the%20government's%20most%20detailed%20version%20yet%20of%20its%20case%20against%20Trump%2C%20including%20its%20description%20of%20the%20former%20president's%20alleged%20pressure%20campaign%20against%20his%20vice%20president%2C%20Mike%20Pence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defendant%20and%20his%20co-conspirators%20recognized%20that%20Pence%2C%20by%20virtue%20of%20his%20ministerial%20role%20presiding%20over%20the%20January%206%20congressional%20certification%2C%20would%20need%20to%20be%20a%20key%20part%20of%20their%20plan%20to%20obstruct%20the%20certification%20proceeding%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20filing%2C%20signed%20by%20Smith%20and%20Senior%20Assistant%20Special%20Counsel%20Molly%20Gaston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20quotes%20repeatedly%20from%20Pence's%20memoir%2C%20So%20Help%20Me%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20from%20internal%20memos%20in%20which%20Trump's%20co-conspirators%20%26quot%3Boutlined%20a%20plan%20for%20Pence%20to%20'gavel'%20in%20the%20defendant%20as%20winner%20of%20the%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20failed%20plan%2C%20Pence%20would%20assert%20the%20false%20claim%20that%20%26quot%3B7%20states%20have%20transmitted%20dual%20slates%20of%20electors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20says%2C%20quoting%20from%20one%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20plan%2C%20prosecutors%20say%2C%20Pence%20would%20then%20use%20that%20invented%20dispute%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20essentially%20unilaterally%20anoint%20Trump%20as%20the%20victor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20his%20co-conspirators%20knew%20Pence%20had%20no%20authority%20to%20do%20so%2C%20Gaston%20wrote.%20And%20at%20least%20two%20co-conspirators%20knew%20they%20needed%20to%20hide%20their%20plotting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20one%20asked%20in%20a%20text%20message%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20Pence%20really%20likely%20to%20be%20on%20board%20with%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20another%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20keep%20this%20off%20text%20for%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPence%20continued%20to%20push%20back%20against%20the%20plan%20throughout%20the%20end%20of%20December%202020%2C%20even%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20defendant%20began%20to%20directly%20and%20repeatedly%20pressure%20Pence%20at%20the%20same%20time%20that%20he%20continued%20summoning%20his%20supporters%20to%20amass%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20congressional%20certification%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20change%20the%20outcome%2C%26quot%3B%20Pence%20told%20Trump%2C%20a%20quotation%20Gaston%20lifts%20from%20and%20credits%20to%20Pence's%20memoir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2028%2C%20Trump%20told%20Pence%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20thousands%26quot%3B%20of%20people%20%26quot%3Bare%20gone%20hate%20your%20guts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20says%2C%20again%20quoting%20from%20the%20memoir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20too%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20complained%2C%20according%20to%20Pence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20gonna%20have%20to%20say%20you%20did%20a%20great%20disservice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20%E2%80%94%20again%20quoting%20from%20the%20memoir%20%E2%80%94%20says%20Trump%20threatened%20his%20balking%20vice%20president%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20lon%20January%205%2C%20a%20day%20before%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20gotta%20be%20tough%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20also%20allegedly%20warned%2C%20in%20another%20call%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThirty%20minutes%20later%2C%20at%2010%20p.m.%2C%20Trump%20issued%20a%20false%20public%20statement%20reading%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Vice%20President%20and%20I%20are%20in%20total%20agreement%20that%20the%20Vice%20President%20has%20the%20power%20to%20act.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20knew%20from%20Pence's%20repeated%20refusals%20that%20this%20was%20a%20lie%2C%20but%20said%20it%20to%20exert%20further%20pressure%2C%20Gaston%20writes.%20At%201%20a.m.%20on%20January%206%2C%20Trump%20exerted%20still%20more%20pressure%2C%20falsely%20tweeting%20%26quot%3BIf%20Vice%20President%20%40Mike_Pence%20comes%20through%20for%20us%2C%20we%20will%20win%20the%20Presidency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20final%20attempt%20to%20pressure%20Pence%20directly%20failed%20later%20that%20morning%2C%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bsent%20to%20the%20Capitol%20a%20crowd%20of%20angry%20supporters%2C%20whom%20the%20defendant%20had%20called%20to%20the%20city%20and%20inundated%20with%20false%20claims%20of%20outcome-determinative%20election%20fraud%2C%20to%20induce%20Pence%20not%20to%20certify%20the%20legitimate%20electoral%20votes%20and%20to%20obstruct%20the%20certification%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20says%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20and%20Mike%20Pence%20at%20a%20campaign%20event%20in%20Minnesota%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cf8fd8a610a9069d59de0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20greeting%20Vice%20President%20Mike%20Pence.%3Cp%3EGlen%20Stubbe%2FStar%20Tribune%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc3f17df-2c0c-415e-849c-709c198c37ed%5C%22%3ETrump's%20communications%20with%20Pence%20are%20not%20official%20conduct.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20Smith%20details%20in%20his%20motion%20why%20prosecutors%20believe%20the%20then-vice%20president's%20discussions%20with%20Trump%20should%20not%20be%20classified%20as%20official%20presidential%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20conduct%20alleged%20in%20the%20original%20indictment%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20was%20official%2C%20and%20subject%20to%20at%20least%20a%20rebuttable%20presumption%20of%20immunity%2C%20was%20the%20defendant's%20attempts%20to%20lie%20to%20and%20pressure%20Vice%20President%20Pence%20to%20misuse%20his%20role%20as%20President%20of%20the%20Senate%20at%20the%20congressional%20certification%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3B%5Bw%5Dhenever%20the%20President%20and%20Vice%20President%20discuss%20their%20official%20responsibilities%2C%20they%20engage%20in%20official%20conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20disagrees.%20The%20executive%20branch%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20has%20no%20official%20role%20in%20the%20election%20certification%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20Executive%20Branch%20has%20no%20role%20in%20the%20certification%20proceeding%E2%80%94and%20indeed%2C%20the%20President%20was%20purposely%20excluded%20from%20it%20by%20design%E2%80%94prosecuting%20the%20defendant%20for%20his%20corrupt%20efforts%20regarding%20Pence%20poses%20no%20danger%20to%20the%20executive%20branch's%20authority%20of%20functioning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223586%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e74bafd17aa3c7b2b2b618%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222391%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump.%