rn%20Israel%20for%20the%20past%20year%2C%20in%20part%20because%20Hezbollah%20fighters%20on%20the%20border%20can%20fire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.i24news.tv%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fisrael-at-war%2Fartc-anti-tank-missile-wounds-3-in-northern-israel-as-tensions-rise%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanti-tank%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20directly%20into%20Israeli%20houses.%20Under%20pressure%20to%20do%20something%2C%20the%20government%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20authorized%20a%20ground%20invasion%20to%20clear%20Hezbollah%20from%20the%20border%20and%20reassure%20Israelis%20that%20they%20can%20return%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20Israeli%20troops%20will%20face%20a%20familiar%20battlefield.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cia.gov%2Freadingroom%2Fdocs%2FCIA-RDP87T01127R000300240004-5.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHilly%20terrain%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20is%20less%20than%20ideal%20for%20movement%20by%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20and%20dotted%20with%20villages%20whose%20mostly%20Shia%20inhabitants%20are%20inclined%20to%20support%20Hezbollah%20(and%20in%20some%20cases%20are%20part-time%20Hezbollah%20fighters).%20Hezbollah%20has%20had%20decades%20to%20fortify%20the%20area%2C%20especially%20with%20an%20elaborate%20network%20of%20tunnels%20similar%20to%20what%20Hamas%20has%20used%20to%20great%20effect%20in%20Gaza.%20Well-trained%20Hezbollah%20fighters%2C%20equipped%20with%20Russian-%20and%20Iranian-made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhezbollah-has-the-firepower-to-ambush-israeli-tanks-in-lebanon-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanti-tank%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20can%20pop%20up%20from%20hidden%20tunnel%20entrances%20and%20fire%20a%20missile%2C%20forcing%20the%20IDF%20into%20a%20whack-a-mole%20war.%20While%20the%20decimation%20of%20Hezbollah's%20leadership%20will%20hamper%20its%20effectiveness%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20its%20members%20are%20trained%20to%20operate%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20IDF%20releases%20footage%20showing%20the%2036th%20Division%20entering%20Lebanon.%20Currently%20two%20IDF%20divisions%20are%20operating%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%2C%20to%20dismantle%20Hezbollah%20infrastructure%20there.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2S0qw1pBaJ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2S0qw1pBaJ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Emanuel%20(Mannie)%20Fabian%20(%40manniefabian)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanniefabian%2Fstatus%2F1841478814905319737%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Israel%20appears%20to%20have%20learned%20some%20lessons%20from%20its%20past%20failures.%20Instead%20of%20tanks%20charging%20across%20into%20the%20border%20into%20Hezbollah%20ambushes%2C%20the%20IDF%20has%20sent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fallisrael.com%2Frevealed-idf-destroyed-700-hezbollah-targets-including-tunnels-in-commando-raids-over-the-past-year%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommando%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20reconnoiter%20the%20terrain%20and%20destroy%20weapons%20and%20fortifications%20to%20prep%20the%20ground%20before%20the%20tanks%20and%20infantry%20go%20in.%20This%20approach%20still%20has%20its%20dangers.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20eight%20IDF%20soldiers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmanniefabian%2Fstatus%2F1841485941820563917%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewere%3C%2Fa%3E%20killed%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%2C%20a%20toll%20that%20includes%20six%20troops%20with%20the%20elite%20Egoz%20Commando%20Unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20intriguing%20question%20is%20the%20depth%20of%20Israeli%20intelligence%20on%20Hezbollah's%20forces%20and%20infrastructure%20in%20southern%20Lebanon.%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20took%20elaborate%20precautions%20to%20keep%20his%20whereabouts%20secret%2C%20yet%20after%20two%20decades%20of%20painstaking%20intelligence%20collection%2C%20Israel%20managed%20to%20pinpoint%20Nasrallah's%20location%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F09%2F28%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fwhy-israel-assassinate-nasrallah.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eassassinate%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20with%20an%20airstrike.%20Such%20deep%20penetration%20into%20Hezbollah's%20innermost%20secrets%20suggests%20that%20Israel%20may%20also%20have%20amassed%20solid%20information%20on%20Hezbollah's%20presence%20on%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20these%20are%20tactical%20considerations.%20The%20dilemma%20for%20Israel%20is%20strategic.%20If%20it%20carries%20out%20a%20short%20ground%20campaign%20to%20cripple%20Hezbollah's%20presence%20on%20Israel's%20border%2C%20then%20the%20moment%20the%20IDF%20leaves%20is%20when%20Hezbollah%20will%20return%20to%20fire%20at%20Israeli%20towns%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dilemma%20it%20has%20also%20seen%20in%20Gaza%20where%20Hamas%20militants%20have%20returned%20to%20areas%20cleared%20by%20Israeli%20soldiers.%20If%20Israel%20creates%20another%20security%20zone%2C%20then%20instead%20of%20Israeli%20civilians%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Israeli%20soldiers%20being%20picked%20off.%20And%20hovering%20over%20those%20hills%20are%20the%20specters%20from%2040%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20what%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20short%20campaign%20dragged%20into%20a%2015-year%20occupation%20that%20killed%20over%20250%20soldiers%20and%20fractured%20Israeli%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20quite%20possible%20that%20a%20ceasefire%20will%20emerge%2C%20most%20likely%20resulting%20in%20an%20uneasy%20calm%20interrupted%20by%20bouts%20of%20violence.%20It%20is%20also%20possible%20that%20a%20short%20war%20may%20become