ium%20Management%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665de2221cd3b17790428866%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPatrick%20McMullan%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMillennium%20Management%20has%20lost%20money%20in%20just%20one%20year%20since%20its%201989%20founding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%2469%20billion%20hedge%20fund%20uses%20a%20strict%20trading%20strategy%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20consistently%20makes%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20trading%20strategy%20has%20helped%20founder%20Israel%20Englander%20become%20a%20billionaire.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2469%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhedge-funds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMillennium%20Management%20hedge%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20employs%20a%20simple%20yet%20effective%20trading%20strategy%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20almost%20always%20makes%20money%20in%20the%20stock%20market%3A%20cut%20losing%20stock%20positions%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20hedge%20funds%20in%20the%20world%2C%20was%20founded%20in%201989%20and%20since%20then%20has%20lost%20money%20in%20just%20a%20single%20year%20%E2%80%94%202008%2C%20when%20a%20financial%20crisis%20turned%20into%20a%20sharp%20recession%20and%20sent%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20crashing%2038%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%20still%20managed%20to%20massively%20outperform%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20that%20year%2C%20shedding%20just%203.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20that%20outlier%20year%2C%20Millennium%20has%20posted%20gains%20every%20single%20year%20of%20its%2035-year%20history%2C%20racking%20up%20%2456%20billion%20in%20cumulative%20profits%20for%20its%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20was%20down%2010%25%20in%202000%20as%20the%20dot-com%20bust%20got%20underway%2C%20Millennium%20saw%20its%20best%20year%20ever%2C%20delivering%20a%2035%25%20return%20for%20its%20investors%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Bloomberg.%20And%20in%202022%2C%20when%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20finished%20the%20year%20down%2019%25%2C%20Millennium%20was%20up%2012%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consistent%20string%20of%20positive%20returns%20at%20Millennium%20stems%20from%20it's%20being%20a%20multi-strategy%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20its%202%2C600%20traders%2C%20investment%20analysts%2C%20and%20portfolio%20managers%20run%20independent%20groups%20concurrently%20using%20various%20investment%20strategies%20across%20stocks%2C%20bonds%2C%20options%2C%20and%20commodities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ffinance%2Finvesting%2Fthe-giant-hedge-fund-that-hates-risk-and-still-wins-1110e90a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20game%20is%20simple%3A%20make%20money%20and%20stay%20employed%2C%20or%20lose%20money%20and%20probably%20get%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20when%20a%20Millennium%20portfolio%20manager%20that%20manages%20%241%20billion%20loses%20%2450%20million%2C%20or%205%25%2C%20the%20first%20threshold%20is%20reached%20and%20that%20manager's%20pool%20of%20available%20capital%20to%20trade%20is%20slashed%20in%20half%2C%20to%20%24500%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20if%20the%20portfolio%20manager%20loses%20an%20additional%20%2425%20million%2C%20or%20a%20total%20of%207.5%25%20on%20the%20initial%20%241%20billion%20allocated%20to%20them%2C%20they%20will%20likely%20be%20fired%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20sometimes%20exceptions%20are%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20strict%20stop-loss%20trading%20strategy%20means%20the%20hedge%20fund%20goes%20through%20a%20lot%20of%20employees%2C%20sporting%20a%20high%20turnover%20rate%20of%20about%2015%25-20%25%20of%20its%20staff%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20trading%20strategy%20is%20also%20what%20turned%20its%20founder%2C%20Israel%20Englander%2C%20into%20a%20billionaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20Bloomberg%2C%20Englander%20is%20worth%20%2413.3%20billion%2C%20making%20him%20the%20172nd%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20strategy%20is%20still%20working.%20Millennium%20posted%20returns%20of%20about%2010%25%20in%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseptember-hedge-fund-performance-exoduspoint-citadel-millennium-point72-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20year-to-date%20it%20is%20up%20another%209.5%25.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillennium%20Management%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-strategy-never-lose-money-in-the-stock-market-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727897853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fda0015ccfc192a552b354%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fhedge-fund-strategy-never-lose-money-in-the-stock-market-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Millennium%20Management's%20%2469%20billion%20hedge%20fund%20has%20lost%20money%20in%20just%20one%20year%20since%20its%201989%20founding%20by%20employing%20this%20stock%20market%20strategy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fhedge-fund-strategy-never-lose-money-in-the-stock-market-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%2010%20most%20comfortable