.com%2F66fd91b47de5c8fd4834bf0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESheehan%20is%20set%20to%20be%20a%20fully-qualified%20plumber%20in%202025%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Teddy%20Sheehan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20me%20to%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20crowd%20and%20get%20noticed.%20We%20asked%20ourselves%20what%20workmen%20like%20and%20came%20up%20with%20hot%20breakfasts.%20Getting%20their%20attention%20through%20their%20stomachs%20seemed%20like%20a%20good%20strategy.%20And%20where%20do%20you%20find%20plumbers%3F%20Plumbers'%20merchants%2C%20where%20they%20buy%20their%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDad%20and%20I%20made%20a%20list%20of%20hardware%20stores%20that%20mostly%20catered%20to%20tradespeople.%20They%20were%20all%20within%20a%2010-mile%20radius%20of%20our%20house.%20Then%2C%20we%20laminated%20200%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-remove-from-resume-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecopies%20of%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20which%20included%20my%20work%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20to%20distribute%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20merchants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20night%20for%20a%20week%2C%20Dad%20and%20I%20prepared%20giant-size%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-british-sausage-rolls-holiday-party-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epigs%20in%20a%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20listened%20to%20playlists%20in%20the%20kitchen%20while%20we%20put%20together%20the%20sausage%20meat%20and%20pastry.%20Then%2C%20at%20around%205%3A30%20a.m.%20the%20next%20day%2C%20we'd%20bake%20the%20batch%20of%20around%2045%20breakfast%20snacks%20in%20the%20oven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20kept%20them%20warm%20in%20insulator%20containers%20and%20drove%20to%20each%20plumber%20merchant%2C%20starting%20at%207%20a.m.%20We'd%20give%20some%20to%20the%20merchants%20and%20ask%20if%20we%20could%20put%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20on%20th