equences%2C%20it%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20enacted%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Religious%20Conversion%20Act%2C%202021%2C%20specifically%20to%20combat%20illegal%20conversions%20through%20%26quot%3BLove%20Jihad.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20grants%20every%20individual%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20practice%20and%20propagate%20their%20religion%2C%20and%20this%20personal%20freedom%20cannot%20be%20compromised%20through%20illegal%20conversions%20facilitated%20by%20'Love%20Jihad'%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727894700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fcourt-generic_625x300_1527245477936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flove-jihad-big-threat-to-nations-unity-says-up-court-sentences-man-6699686%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20objective%20of%20%26quot%3Blove%20jihad%26quot%3B%20is%20to%20establish%20dominance%20by%20certain%20anti-social%20elements%20of%20a%20particular%20religion%20against%20India%20through%20demographic%20warfare%20and%20international%20conspiracy%2C%20a%20local%20court%20here%20has%20observed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ananya%20once%20burned%20her%20ex-BF's%20photo%20after%20breakup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727894534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113884876%2Cimgsize-20416.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fananya-panday-confesses-she-once-burned-her-ex-boyfriends-photo-after-breakup-i-relate-to