TION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20the%20IDF%20or%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%2C%20the%20Ambassador%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BFortunately%20we%20have%20not%20had%20any%20loss%20of%20life%20in%20Israel%20and%20not%20much%20damage%20either.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20there%20was%20a%20tragic%20loss%20of%20life%20of%20a%20Palestinian%20national%20from%20Gaza%20where%20an%20Iranian%20missile%20hit.%20Iran's%20missile%20killed%20a%20Palestinian.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20giving%20details%20of%20a%20likely%20counter-attack%2C%20Mr%20Azar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20challenge%20here%20because%20these%20kinds%20of%20radical%20people%20cannot%20be%20deterred.%20We%20have%20seen%20that%20time%20and%20time%20again.%20When%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20terror%20attack%20on%20us%20or%20when%20Nasrallah%20decided%20to%20attack%20Israel%20for%2011%20months%2C%20they%20do%20not%20even%20care%20for%20their%20own%20people%2C%20putting%20their%20lives%20in%20danger.%20We%20have%20to%20give%20a%20serious%20blow%20to%20these%20extremists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambassador%20further%20clarified%20that%20Israel%20is%20not%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Iran%2C%20and%20neither%20are%20they%20in%20the%20business%20of%20installing%20regimes%20in%20other%20countries.%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20only%20defends%20itself%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BWe%20put%20our%20lives%20on%20the%20line%20to%20defend%20our%20country%2C%20not%20to%20change%20political%20realities%20in%20other%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20however%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20past%20how%20Iranian%20people%20have%20revolted%20against%20the%20radical%20regime.%20Change%20will%20not%20come%20from%20outside%2C%20it%20will%20come%20from%20within%2C%20if%20it%20does.%20As%20for%20Israel%20-%20we%20are%20only%20going%20to%20engage%20to%20the%20level%20of%20security%20of%20our%20people%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20of%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20have%20shared%20friendly%20ties%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%20Iran%20is%20not%20the%20enemy%20of%20Israel.%20The%20Persian%20people%20have%20a%20rich%20history%2C%20an%20ancient%20civilisation%2C%20which%20used%20to%20have%20amazing%20connect%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Azar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20a%20situation%20where%20our%20threat%20to%20national%20security%20is%20dealt%20with%20effectively%2C%20a%20situation%20where%20our%20people%20can%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20in%20northern%20Israel%2C%20we%20want%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20resolutions%201701%20and%201559%20can%20be%20effectively%20implemented.%20Israel%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20an%20occupying%20force%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20neither%20does%20Israel%20want%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20political%20future%20of%20Lebanon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20envoy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDISAPPOINTMENT%20WITH%20UNITED%20NATIONS%20SECRETARY%20GENERAL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20UN%20chief%2C%20the%20Ambassador%20said%20the%20United%20Nations%20are%20doing%20very%20good%20work%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bunfortunately%20there%20are%20blocs%20within%20the%20United%20Nations%20that%20are%20biased.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20there%20is%20a%20rigged%20system%20in%20place%20at%20the%20UN%2C%20wherein%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20countries%20can%20manipulate%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20UN%20such%2C%20that%20you%20have%20a%20Secretary%20General%20of%20the%20UN%20who%20is%20not%20condemning%20this%20terrible%20barrage%20of%20missiles%2C%20it%20is%20very%20very%20worrisome.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20UN%20should%20be%20neutral%20and%20unbiased%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20envoy%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAN%20INDIA%20PLAY%20A%20ROLE%20IN%20BRINGING%20PEACE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20India%20can%20play%20a%20diplomatic%20role%20to%20bring%20peace%20to%20the%20region%2C%20the%20Israeli%20envoy%20said%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20for%20India%20to%20decide.%20Diplomacy%20can%20always%20work.%20We%20initially%20tried%20to%20resolve%20issues%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%20via%20diplomatic%20channels%2C%20but%20that%20didn%3Bt%20work.%20Sometimes%20when%20there%20are%20extremist%20regimes%2C%20in%20order%20to%20defend%20oneself%2C%20one%20has%20to%20deal%20with%20it%20strongly%20to%20be%20effective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20India%20is%20an%20important%20player%20and%20a%20friend%20of%20Israel's%2C%20and%20New%20Delhi%20will%20definitely%20help%20in%20building%20back%20the%20Middle%20East%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcorridor%20of%20stability%20-%20one%20that%20connects%20Asia%20and%20Europe%26quot%3B.%20India%20is%20a%20partner%20of%20Israel%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETIES%20WITH%20THE%20ARAB%20NATIONS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20envoy%20highlighted%20that%20in%20the%20nearly%20year-long%20crisis%20in%20West%20Asia%2C%20and%20Israel's%20efforts%20to%20safeguard%20itself%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20single%20Arab%20country%20has%20broken%20ties%20with%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20during%20this%20year%20Israel%20has%20been%20building%20its%20security%20cooperation%20and%20its%20intelligence%20cooperation%20across%20the%20Middle%20East.%20What%20does%20that%20show...%20that%20when%20this%20conflict%20is%20over%2C%20all%20these%20nations%20which%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20building%20a%20peaceful%20and%20progressive%20Middle%20East%20will%20work%20together%20to%20achieve%20that.%20It%20shows%20that%20there%20is%20an%20alternative%20to%20extremism%2C%20to%20fanaticism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20closing%20remarks%2C%20the%20Ambassador%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20%26quot%3BHamas%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20threat%20to%20Israel%2C%20Hezbollah%20has%20faced%20a%20serious%20blow%2C%20and%20Iran%20will%20now%20pay%20for%20what%20it%20has%20done.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727884440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F8giaa6mc_israel-ambassador-reuven-azar-ndtv-interview_625x300_02_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-whats-next-for-israel-after-iran-missile-attack-envoy-explains-6701952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iran's%20attack%20on%20Israel%20wasn't%20just%20a%20barrage%20of%20missiles%2C%20it%20was%20a%20barrage%20of%20181%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20each%20having%20a%20warhead%20payload%20of%20between%20700-1%2C000%20kilograms.%20It%20is%20unprecedented%2C%20Israel's%20Ambassador%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-whats-next-for-israel-after-iran-missile-attack-envoy-explains-6701952%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Analysing%20where%20Iran's%20missiles%20struck%20in%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727884167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F9db6%2Flive%2F73883370-80d5-11ef-ad45-893aa022fcbc.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcr4x3xnn7w7o%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BBC%20Verify%20analysed%20three%20locations%20that%20were%20hit%20by%20Iranian%20missiles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcr4x3xnn7w7o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Triptii%20faces%20fresh%20backlash%20after%20confirmation%20video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727883608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113882171%2Cimgsize-46174.cms%22%2C%22orig