%20with%20Gilead%20to%20manufacture%2C%20commercialise%20HIV%20drug%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727879764000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F27%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1719512062-3108.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fhealth%2Fdr-reddy-s-ties-up-with-gilead-to-manufacture-commercialise-hiv-drug-124100200779_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20has%20entered%20into%20a%20royalty-free%20non-exclusive%20voluntary%20licensing%20agreement%20with%20Gilead%20Sciences%20Ireland%20UC%20for%20the%20drug%2C%20the%20Hyderabad-based%20drug%20maker%20said%20in%20a%20statement%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fhealth%2Fdr-reddy-s-ties-up-with-gilead-to-manufacture-commercialise-hiv-drug-124100200779_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fhealth%2Fdr-reddy-s-ties-up-with-gilead-to-manufacture-commercialise-hiv-drug-124100200779_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fhealth%2Fdr-reddy-s-ties-up-with-gilead-to-manufacture-commercialise-hiv-drug-124100200779_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pawar%20vs%20Pawar%20Battle%20In%20Supreme%20Court%20Over%20Clock%20Symbol%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20battle%20over%20the%20clock%20-%20the%20election%20symbol%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20-%20has%20heated%20up%20again%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20party%20approaching%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20has%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20stop%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20from%20using%20the%20%26quot%3Bclock%26quot%3B%20symbol.%20The%20court%20will%20hear%20the%20petition%20on%20October%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20has%20said%20the%20use%20of%20the%20clock%20by%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20earlier%20this%20year%20had%20caused%20considerable%20confusion%20among%20voters.%20They%20have%20appealed%20that%20a%20new%20symbol%20be%20grated%20to%20the%20other%20side.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20NCP%20name%20and%20poll%20symbol%20was%20awarded%20to%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20party%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20after%20Pawar%20Junior%20rebelled%20against%20his%20uncle%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20July%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20ahead%20of%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20barred%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20from%20using%20the%20clock%20symbol%20and%20ordered%20that%20they%20make%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20people%20that%20the%20symbol%20was%20sub%20judice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20voters%20made%20it%20clear%20who%20they%20thought%20was%20the%20real%20NCP.%20The%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20won%20eight%20seats%20compared%20to%20the%20single%20seat%20won%20by%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20other%20party%20for%20which%20the%20Election%20Commission%20used%20a%20similar%20formula%20--%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20which%20had%20also%20split%20-%20also%20received%20a%20similar%20message%20from%20the%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20was%20dismal%20for%20the%20ruling%20alliance%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20-the%20alliance%20of%20Congress%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20-%20winning%2030%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20seats.%20The%20ruling%20alliance%20won%2017.%20One%20seat%20went%20to%20an%20Independent%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20has%20been%20facing%20setbacks%20since%20with%20a%20section%20of%20their%20leaders%20quitting%20and%20returning%20to%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20has%20also%20filed%20an%20appeal%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20challenging%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20decision%20to%20recognise%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20as%20the%20real%20NCP%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20being%20heard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727878200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fra0i1bhg_sharad-pawar-ajit-pawar_625x300_05_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpawar-vs-pawar-battle-in-supreme-court-over-clock-symbol-6701123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20battle%20over%20the%20clock%20-%20the%20election%20symbol%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20-%20has%20heated%20up%20again%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20party%20approaching%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpawar-vs-pawar-battle-in-supreme-court-over-clock-symbol-6701123%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mithun%3A%20I%20became%20arrogant%20after%20National%20Award%20win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727877834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113880629%2Cimgsize-23144.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmithun-chakraborty-confesses-he-became-arrogant-after-winning-national-award-for-mrigayaa-producer-ne-bola-get-out%2Farticleshow%2F113880627.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113880627.cms%5C%22%2