5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20his%20brother%20and%20father%20Naushad's%20car%20accident%20had%20perturbed%20him%2C%20it%20didn't%20seem%20so%20in%20his%20batting%20as%20he%20went%20hammer%20and%20tongs%20at%20the%20Rest%20of%20India%20bowling%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20played%20160%20dot%20balls%20but%20still%20maintained%20a%2080%20percent%20strike-rate%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20his%2025%20boundaries%20and%20four%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajinkya%20Rahane%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F965-ajinkya-rahane-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjinkya%20Rahane%3C%2Fa%3E%20(97%20off%20234%20balls)%20missed%20out%20on%20a%2040th%20first-class%20hundred%20but%20the%20second%20day%20belonged%20to%20Sarfaraz%2C%20who%20was%20in%20a%20mood%20to%20punish%20pacers%20and%20spinners%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%2015th%20first-class%20century%20will%20certainly%20dispel%20all%20doubts%20about%20his%20slot%20as%20reserve%20middle-order%20batter%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20Test%20season%20(8%20games).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%2C%20who%20got%20back%20his%20middle-order%20slot%20from%20Sarfaraz%2C%20did%20well%20in%20Kanpur%20but%20the%20team%20management%20and%20even%20the%20Karnataka%20batter%20knows%20that%20the%20stockily%20built%20Mumbaikar%20is%20breathing%20down%20his%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ekana%20Stadium%20track%20had%20underlying%20moisture%20on%20the%20second%20day%20and%20the%20dampness%20contributed%20to%20ball%20seaming%20around%20initially%20and%20the%20extra%20bounce%20made%20it%20challenging%20for%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20driving%20on%20the%20off-side%20was%20regal%20while%20there%20is%20nothing%20more%20to%20add%20to%20his%20footwork%20against%20spinners.%20He%20was%20brutal%2C%20especially%20against%20left-arm%20spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Manav%20Suthar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F115314-manav-suthar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMana