%94%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Gujarat%20Ecology%20Commission%20(GEC)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20implemented%20through%20a%20community-based%20village%20organisation%20across%20more%20than%20150%20hectares%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompleted%20in%202015%2C%20the%20mangroves%20have%20since%20become%20vital%20to%20the%20villagers%2C%20providing%20resources%20such%20as%20fodder%2C%20fuelwood%2C%20and%20supporting%20fishing%20activities.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20mangroves%20act%20as%20a%20natural%20barrier%2C%20preventing%20saltwater%20from%20encroaching%20on%20farmlands%20and%20protecting%20crops%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20improves%20crop%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20focus%2C%20in%20line%20with%20ESG%20(Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Governance)%20parameters%2C%20is%20to%20minimise%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20their%20manufacturing%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20processes.%20Through%20green%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Blue%20Carbon%20project%2C%20it%20is%20actively%20working%20towards%20achieving%20carbon%20neutrality%20by%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20waves%20%E2%80%94%20environmentally%20and%20economically%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20are%20vital%20tropical%20plants%20that%20thrive%20in%20coastal%20ecosystems%20under%20conditions%20most%20timber%20cannot%20tolerate.%20They%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20storing%20large%20amounts%20of%20carbon%20and%20protecting%20shorelines%20and%20their%20inhabitants%20from%20damaging%20winds%2C%20waves%2C%20and%20floods.%20Additionally%2C%20mangroves%20help%20prevent%20salinity%20and%20seawater%20intrusion%20into%20agricultural%20areas%2C%20improving%20crop%20quality%20and%20enabling%20farmers%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%204000px)%20100vw%2C%204000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG_0780_11zo