elf%20some%3Cem%3E%20matar%20khasta%20%3C%2Fem%3Erolls%20(fried%20finger%20food%20with%20green%20pea%20filling)%20while%20I%20regale%20you%20with%20a%20history%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIF.BE%E2%80%99s%20walls%2C%20150%20years%20ago%2C%20would%20be%20privy%20to%20conversations%20of%20factory%20workers%20that%20ranged%20from%20whether%20the%20gantry%20was%20working%20properly%20to%20concerns%20about%20being%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20ice%20demand%20of%20fish%20markets%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F72036%2Fmumbai-cafe-military-iconic-widely-loved-why%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Bombay%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbico%20Ice%20Factory%20(as%20it%20was%20known%20then)%20enjoyed%20its%20popularity%20for%20decades%20before%20a%20factory%20in%20New%20Bombay%20took%20over%20operations.%20%E2%80%9CIce%20first%20came%20to%20India%20on%20a%20ship%20from%20Boston%20in%20the%201800s%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zon-1726747066.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20banyan%20tree%20at%20the%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20caught%20Kamal%20Malik's%20attention%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20restore%20the%20place%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zon-1726747066.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zon-1726747066-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zon-1726747066-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zo