ainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366752%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIF.BE%20boasts%20five%20sections%20which%20include%20a%20fine-dining%20restaurant%2C%20a%20cafe%2C%20a%20space%20for%20exhibitions%2C%20a%20space%20for%20performances%2C%20and%20a%20reading%20room%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20that%20took%20the%20most%20amount%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20Malik%20shares%2C%20was%20the%20main%20Ice%20Factory%2C%20sub-station%2C%20cold%20storage%2C%20and%20the%20ice-cubing%20area.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20required%20intensive%20examination%20and%20surgical%20intervention%20through%20retrofits%20to%20stabilise%20crumbling%2C%20warped%2C%20and%20leaking%20walls%2C%20sagging%20roofs%20and%20trusses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20every%20adventure%20story%2C%20the%20most%20exciting%20part%20is%20when%20a%20treasure%20is%20discovered.%20When%20the%20team%20stumbled%20upon%20giant%20cooling%20coils%20that%20were%20once%20used%20to%20manufacture%20ice%2C%20they%20were%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20re